# MY MENU

3. Select a menu to be registered and press the **MENU/OK** button. Press the **MENU/OK** button again to return to the menu selection screen.

4. Select a menu to be registered next and press the **MENU/OK** button. Select the order of the menus to be registered and press the **MENU/OK** button.

!Select Item Location

5. Repeat Step 4 and register “my menu”. To exit “my menu” registration, press the **DISP/BACK** button.

> 💡 **Note:**  
> “My menu” can contain up to 16 items.
